description:
Darkness Radio presents Supernatural News/ParaShare Paranormal Phenomena...do do do, do do! Edition.

Dave & Tim roll out a rant or 2, share some laughs, listeners paranormal emails and the strange supernatural news from around the world! Creepy phenomena caught on camera, a toddler responds to a ghost calling out for help and another ghostly voice recorded wondering why the people living there just won't die! The boys discuss the Battersea Poltergeist, UFO Disclosure, and more! Plus a Theater of the Mind.
